{"type":"message","id":"c20a5cbf","parentId":"8bf329c8","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:17:35.962Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_46d62c5e8c9842b4be713488","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 设置白平衡模式\r\n// 白平衡模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\r\nfunction onWbModeChange(mode) {\r\n    var manualControls = document.getElementById('wbManualControls');\r\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('wbLocalControls');\r\n    var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n    var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n\r\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'flex';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = false;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = false;\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\r\n        // v8.39: 局部模式自动切换到手动模式\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 自动\r\n        if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\r\n        if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\r\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('auto');\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 停止自动白平衡\r\nfunction stopAutoWhiteBalance() {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('用户停止', 'warning');\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop', {}).then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n            showToast('success', '已停止白平衡搜索');\r\n        }\r\n\n[787 more lines in file. Use offset=1289 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783379855962}}
{"type":"message","id":"7c0381b7","parentId":"c20a5cbf","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:17:35.963Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1154665aa8274aa089dae392","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance\", summary=\"设置白平衡\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_whitebalance(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置白平衡参数(模式或R/B增益)。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        # 参数处理\r\n        mode_input = data.get(\"mode\")\r\n        red_input = data.get(\"red_gain\")\r\n        blue_input = data.get(\"blue_gain\")\r\n\r\n        # 获取当前值\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\")\r\n        current_mode = \"auto\"\r\n        current_red = 100\r\n        current_blue = 80\r\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n            for elem in root.iter():\r\n                tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n                if tag == \"WhiteBalanceStyle\":\r\n                    current_mode = (elem.text or \"auto\").lower()\r\n                elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceRed\":\r\n                    current_red = int(elem.text or 100)\r\n                elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceBlue\":\r\n                    current_blue = int(elem.text or 80)\r\n\r\n        # 使用传入值或当前值\r\n        mode_val = mode_input if mode_input else current_mode\r\n        red_val = red_input if red_input is not None else current_red\r\n        blue_val = blue_input if blue_input is not None else current_blue\r\n\r\n        # ISAPI 要求小写\r\n        mode_isapi = mode_val.lower() if mode_val else \"manual\"\r\n\r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<WhiteBalance version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n<WhiteBalanceStyle>{mode_isapi}</WhiteBalanceStyle>\r\n<WhiteBalanceRed>{red_val}</WhiteBalanceRed>\r\n<WhiteBalanceBlue>{blue_val}</WhiteBalanceBlue>\r\n</WhiteBalance>'''\r\n\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            log_info(\"image\", \"whitebalance\", {\"device\": device_id, \"mode\": mode_val, \"red\": red_val, \"blue\": blue_val})\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"白平衡已更新\", \"data\": {\"mode\": mode_val, \"red_gain\": red_val, \"blue_gain\": blue_val}}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"更新失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置白平衡异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/noisereduce\", summary=\"获取降噪设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def get_noisereduce(device_id: str) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"获取设备降噪当前设置。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n\n[1317 more lines in file. Use offset=3003 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783379855962}}
{"type":"message","id":"342bb27a","parentId":"7c0381b7","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:18:35.998Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the issue:\n\n1. In `onWbModeChange(mode)` in console.html:\n   - If mode is 'manual': show manual controls, setWhiteBalanceMode('manual')\n   - If mode is 'local': hide manual controls, show local controls, setWhiteBalanceMode('manual')\n   - If mode is 'auto': hide manual controls and local controls, setWhiteBalanceMode('auto')\n\n2. In router.py `set_whitebalance`:\n   - It accepts mode, red_gain, blue_gain\n   - It looks like it should work for all modes\n\nSo the user's issue is likely in one of these places:\n1. The dropdown option values don't match (console.html has 'auto', router expects 'auto' - they match)\n2. The backend ISAPI call to `/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance` doesn't support switching to auto mode\n3. There's some UI state issue\n\nLet me re-read the user's requirement: \"现在切换到区域白平衡之后，再下拉菜单点击选择自动，没有实现切换到自动\"\n\nAh, I think I misunderstood. The user says: \"CenterWhiteBalance\" (区域白平衡) - this is the local/zone white balance mode. The user switches to local/zone white balance mode, then tries to select \"auto\" from the dropdown, but it doesn't switch to auto mode.\n\nLooking at console.html line 260:\n```html\n<select id=\"wbMode\" ... onchange=\"onWbModeChange(this.value)\">\n    <option value=\"auto\">自动</option>\n    <option value=\"manual\">手动</option>\n    <option value=\"local\">局部</option>\n</select>\n```\n\nAnd the code in onWbModeChange:\n```javascript\n} else {\n    // 自动\n    if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\n    if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\n    setWhiteBalanceMode('auto');\n}\n```\n\nI see the problem now. When switching to the 'local' mode, the user attempts to select 'auto', but the previous implementation doesn't handle this specific transition correctly. The dropdown selection seems to be getting stuck or not propagating the intended 'auto' mode change.\n\nThe current implementation only supports direct mode switching without preserving the user's desired mode change. It completely disables both manual and local controls when selecting 'auto', effectively preventing any further interaction with the white balance settings.\n\nI see a critical design flaw that blocks the expected user interaction flow. The code needs modification to allow selecting 'auto' when 'local' mode is active, ensuring more flexible control visibility.\n\nThe core intent requires implementing a nuanced white balance mode selection mechanism that respects different control contexts while maintaining simplicity.\n\nMy proposed solution focuses on a targeted modification in the `onWbModeChange` function, specifically handling the edge case where users transition between sub-modes like 'local' and desire a broader 'auto' mode selection.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我现在已经读取了所有需要的文件。让我分析问题：\n\n## 问题分析\n\n### 问题1-3是对焦和白平衡的逻辑修复\n### 问题4：白平衡\"区域白平衡\"后选择\"自动\"不生效\n\n**根因**：console.html的`onWbModeChange(mode)`只处理'auto' → 隐藏所有控件的方式，但没有处理在'local'模式下重新选择'auto'的情况。\n\n当前代码（console.html第1251-1279行）：\n- 'manual' → 显示手动控件\n- 'local' → 显示局部控件（隐藏手动控件）\n- 'auto' → 隐藏所有控件\n\n用户期望：在'local'（区域白平衡）模式下下拉选择'auto' → 应该切换到白自动模式，R/B控件禁用。\n\n### 修复方案\n\n我需要了解用户需求和预期行为。让我先开始前3个修复（对焦和白平衡逻辑），然后再回来处理白平衡切换问题。\n\n让我先读取和修改这两个核心文件。我将立即进行修复。\n\n开始修复对焦算法（autofocus.py），然后白平衡算法。白平衡切换问题我先保留到后面处理。现在开始：立即进行detailed修复计划：\n\n接下来立即进行完整的修复：\n1. 对焦：best1/best2/best3严格排序 + 最佳失败全流程重置\n2. 白平衡：精调模式3档步进（delta>=200→5步，10<=delta<200→2步，delta<10→1步，1步上限30次）\n3. 开始处理白平衡\"区域白平衡\"后切换到\"自动\"的问题\n\n先读取关键代码片段以便精确修改：对焦的_fine阶段、白平衡的step阶段、以及console.html的白平衡切换逻辑。现在开始修复。立即开始修复。先修复对焦算法。现在开始修复。让我先修复对焦算法（autofocus.py）：\n\n**修复要点：**\n1. 增加best1跟踪（扫描峰值）\n2. 成功条件改为：best3 > best2 **或** best3 > best1\n3. 达到10步仍未超越 → 全流程重置（调用_do_retry）\n\n先看_autofocus.py的_init和_step_fine方法。已读取。现在实施修复。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_86f11a96a32745be9c2c999e","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py","edits":[{"newText":"        # 搜索数据\n        self._points = []  # [(position, contrast), ...]\n        self._step_count = 0\n        self._best1_value = 0.0  # 扫描峰值（保留）\n        self._best_value = 0.0   # 当前最佳（可能被样条覆盖）\n        self._best2_value = 0.0   # approach阶段最佳\n        self._best3_value = 0.0   # 0.1s精逼近最佳\n        self._best_pos = 0\n        self._decline_count = 0\n        self._decline_after_best = 0\n\n        # 平坦区域\n        self._flat_reversed = False\n\n        # 回退/精逼近\n        self._optimal_pos = None\n        self._approach_remaining = 0\n        self._approach_dir = 1\n        self._fine_step = 0\n        self._fine_dir = 1\n        self._fine_max_steps = 10","oldText":"        # 扫描数据\n        self._points = []  # [(position, contrast), ...]\n        self._step_count = 0\n        self._best_value = 0.0\n        self._best_pos = 0\n        self._decline_count = 0\n        self._decline_after_best = 0\n\n        # 平坦区域\n        self._flat_reversed = False\n\n        # 结果\n        self._optimal_pos = None\n        self._approach_remaining = 0\n        self._approach_dir = 1\n        # best2 初始化为扫描峰值\n        self._best2_value = 0.0   # approach 阶段初始化为 _best_value\n        self._best3_value = 0.0   # 0.1s 精逼近的 best\n        self._fine_step = 0\n        self._fine_dir = 1\n        self._fine_max_steps = 10"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":50740,"output":1573,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52313,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783379855964,"responseId":"cht000d4b71@dx19f39b90ecf29bb503"}}
