{"type":"message","id":"cd5e39d0","parentId":"2a569e50","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:19:23.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good progress. Now I need to also track best1 during the approach phase. Looking at `_fit_and_search`, before setting `_best_value` to the spline peak, I should save the scan peak as best1. Actually wait, in the `_fit_and_search` function, the `_best1_value` was already set in `_step_scan`. So the scan peak is tracked. But then in `_fit_and_search`, it overwrites `_best_value` with the spline peak.\n\nHmm, actually `_best1_value` is NOT used in the current `_fit_and_search`. It just saves it but doesn't use it anywhere. I need to save `self._best_value` (scan peak/candidate peak) before it gets overwritten.\n\nLet me look at all paths in `_fit_and_search` where `_best_value` is not set:\n\n1. R² < 0.6: depends on current_pos and best_pos - current_pos is near best_pos, so similar to step 2\n2. Spline failed: similar to step 2\n3. Search failed: similar to step 2\n4. `opt_x, opt_y = max(candidates, key=lambda c: c[1])` → this overwrites `_best_old = self._best_value`, then 4 sets `_best_value = opt_y`\n\nSo in case 4 (normal success), `_best_value` gets overwritten. I should save the current best value (scan peak or appro          aching peak) as `_best1_value` before overwriting it.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The \"best1\" should represent the peak found in the SCAN or APPROACH phase before the fine phase. In `_fit_and_search`, the peak could be:\n- The spline peak (overwrites `_best_value`)\n- The original scan peak (when R² < 0.6 or spline failed)\n\n\n- The approach peak\n\nThe approach phase track updates the best value until `_approach_remaining` reaches 0. When moving to the fine phase, I'll set `_best3_value` to the maximum value from both scan and approach phases. This ensures I capture the true best amplitude found so far, regardless of which phase produced it.\n\nThe candidate peak in `_fit_and_search` comes from `golden_section_search`, which narrows the search around the best position. Since `_best_value` was previously set to the scan peak during `_step_scan`, and `_fit_and_search` then looks near that peak, the current approach seems reasonable. I'll preserve this existing logic.\n\nThe fine phase comparison needs to check `_best3_value` against both `_best2_value` and `_best1_value`. Among these, `_best2_value` holds the highest value from scan, approach, and spline phases, while `_best1_value` represents just the original scan peak. This means validating against `_best2_value` already covers the user's requirement.\n\nThe success condition simply states \"best3必须大于之前的best2，或者best1\". Since `_best2_value` captures the maximum value from scan and approach phases, verifying `_best3_value > _best2_value` inherently satisfies the condition for both comparison points.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"现在修改 `_fit_and_search`，保存 scan peak 作为 best1（防止被样条覆盖）："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_46336f53af004abdb4e0db8e","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"        opt_x, opt_y = max(candidates, key=lambda c: c[1])\n        self._best1_value = self._best_value  # 保存扫描峰值\n        self._best_value = opt_y  # 用样条峰值覆盖\n        self._optimal_pos = opt_x","oldText":"        opt_x, opt_y = max(candidates, key=lambda c: c[1])\n        self._best_value = opt_y\n        self._optimal_pos = opt_x"}],"path":"astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":52909,"output":815,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53724,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783379930447,"responseId":"cht000de148@dx19f39ba33132871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"98e3b1b7","parentId":"cd5e39d0","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:19:23.891Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_46336f53af004abdb4e0db8e","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 450                 \"message\": f\"搜索失败,回退到best(剩余{self._approach_remaining}步)\"\n 451             }\n 452 \n 453         opt_x, opt_y = max(candidates, key=lambda c: c[1])\n-454         self._best_value = opt_y\n+454         self._best1_value = self._best_value  # 保存扫描峰值\n+455         self._best_value = opt_y  # 用样条峰值覆盖\n 455         self._optimal_pos = opt_x\n 456 \n 457         # 计算回退步数（整数，每步0.2s，与扫描步长一致）\n 458         current_pos = x_vals[-1]\n     ...","firstChangedLine":454},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783379963891}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc8362e3","parentId":"98e3b1b7","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:19:40.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在修改 `_step_fine`：best3 必须大于 best2 或 best1，否则全流程重置。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d256eef0dfaf433bb3763a16","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"    def _step_fine(self, contrast):\n        \"\"\"精逼近阶段：0.1s步进微调，最多10步。\n        \n        成功条件：best3 > best2 或 best3 > best1\n        失败（10步未达标）：全流程重置\n        \"\"\"\n        self._fine_step += 1\n\n        # 追踪 best3\n        if contrast > self._best3_value:\n            self._best3_value = contrast\n\n        # 成功：best3 > best2 或 best3 > best1\n        if self._best3_value > self._best2_value or self._best3_value > self._best1_value:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            best = max(self._best3_value, self._best2_value, self._best1_value)\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f},best1={self._best1_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": best\n            }\n\n        # 趋势下降 → 反向\n        if contrast < self._best3_value:\n            self._fine_dir = -self._fine_dir\n\n        # 达到最大步数仍未达标 → 全流程重置\n        if self._fine_step >= self._fine_max_steps:\n            if self._do_retry():\n                action = \"focus_near\" if self._direction < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n                dir_name = '近' if self._direction < 0 else '远'\n                return {\n                    \"action\": action, \"duration\": 0.2,\n                    \"stage\": \"scan\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                    \"message\": f\"精逼近未达标(best3={self._best3_value:.1f}≤best2={self._best2_value:.1f}),全流程重启(尝试{self._attempt+1}/3)\"\n                }\n            self._state = self.FAILED\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"error\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦失败(3次重试耗尽,best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f})\"\n            }\n\n        # 继续精逼近\n        action = \"focus_near\" if self._fine_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n        return {\n            \"action\": action, \"duration\": 0.1,\n            \"stage\": \"fine\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"精逼近(步{self._fine_step}/{self._fine_max_steps},best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f})\"\n        }","oldText":"    def _step_fine(self, contrast):\n        \"\"\"精逼近阶段：0.1s步进微调，最多10步，best3必须>best2。\"\"\"\n        self._fine_step += 1\n\n        # 追踪 best3\n        if contrast > self._best3_value:\n            self._best3_value = contrast\n\n        # best3 > best2 → 成功\n        if self._best3_value > self._best2_value:\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦成功(best3={self._best3_value:.1f}>best2={self._best2_value:.1f})\",\n                \"best\": self._best3_value\n            }\n\n        # 趋势下降 → 反向\n        if contrast < self._best3_value:\n            self._fine_dir = -self._fine_dir\n\n        # 达到最大步数\n        if self._fine_step >= self._fine_max_steps:\n            # best3 未超过 best2，取最大值\n            self._state = self.DONE\n            best = max(self._best3_value, self._best2_value)\n            return {\n                \"action\": \"stop\", \"duration\": 0,\n                \"stage\": \"done\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n                \"message\": f\"对焦完成(精逼近{self._fine_step}步,best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f},未达标)\",\n                \"best\": best\n            }\n\n        # 继续精逼近\n        action = \"focus_near\" if self._fine_dir < 0 else \"focus_far\"\n        return {\n            \"action\": action, \"duration\": 0.1,\n            \"stage\": \"fine\", \"contrast\": round(contrast, 2),\n            \"message\": f\"精逼近(步{self._fine_step}/{self._fine_max_steps},best3={self._best3_value:.1f},best2={self._best2_value:.1f})\"\n        }"}],"path":"astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":53389,"output":1276,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54665,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783379963893,"responseId":"cht000df6c2@dx19f39bab1602871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7e9492d3","parentId":"dc8362e3","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:19:40.776Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d256eef0dfaf433bb3763a16","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"edit\",\n  \"error\": \"Could not find the exact text in astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\\nCurrent file contents:\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"AstroHub v8.59 - 反差对焦模块（黄金分割+三次样条）\\r\\n\\r\\n算法流程：\\r\\n1. 扫描：等步长移动焦点，每步截图计算反差 → 收集 (position, contrast) 数据点\\r\\n2. 峰值检测：反差下降N步后确认峰值，停止扫描\\r\\n3. 三次样条拟合：对数据点拟合自然三次样条\\r\\n4. 黄金分割搜索：在样条曲线上精确找峰\\r\\n5. 移动到峰值位置\\r\\n\\r\\n参考：github.com/russwong89/sharpness_detection_autofocus\\r\\n\\\"\\\"\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\nimport json\\r\\nimport asyncio\\r\\nimport math\\r\\nimport numpy as np\\r\\nfrom .region_base import calc_contrast, calc_stable_delay\\r\\n\\r\\n# 黄金分割比例\\r\\nGR = (math.sqrt(5) - 1) / 2\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\nclass CubicSpline:\\r\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"自然三次样条插值。\\r\\n\\r\\n    在数据点之间拟合三次多项式段，\\r\\n    端点处二阶导数=0（自然样条）。\\r\\n    \\\"\\\"\\\"\\r\\n\\r\\n    def __init__(self, x_vals, y_vals):\\r\\n        self.x_vals = np.array(x_vals, dtype=float)\\r\\n        self.y_vals = np.array(y_vals, dtype=float)\\r\\n        self.n = len(x_vals) - 1\\r\\n        self._coeffs = None\\r\\n        self._fit()\\r\\n\\r\\n    def _fit(self):\\r\\n        \\\"\\\"\\\"求解三次样条系数。\\\"\\\"\\\"\\r\\n        n \\n... (truncated)\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"edit","error":"Could not find the exact text in astrohub/src/controlpanel/autofocus.py. The old text must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines.\nCurrent file contents:\n\"\"\"AstroHub v8.59 - 反差对焦模块（黄金分割+三次样条）\r\n\r\n算法流程：\r\n1. 扫描：等步长移动焦点，每步截图计算反差 → 收集 (position, contrast) 数据点\r\n2. 峰值检测：反差下降N步后确认峰值，停止扫描\r\n3. 三次样条拟合：对数据点拟合自然三次样条\r\n4. 黄金分割搜索：在样条曲线上精确找峰\r\n5. 移动到峰值位置\r\n\r\n参考：github.com/russwong89/sharpness_detection_autofocus\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nimport json\r\nimport asyncio\r\nimport math\r\nimport numpy as np\r\nfrom .region_base import calc_contrast, calc_stable_delay\r\n\r\n# 黄金分割比例\r\nGR = (math.sqrt(5) - 1) / 2\r\n\r\n\r\nclass CubicSpline:\r\n    \"\"\"自然三次样条插值。\r\n\r\n    在数据点之间拟合三次多项式段，\r\n    端点处二阶导数=0（自然样条）。\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n\r\n    def __init__(self, x_vals, y_vals):\r\n        self.x_vals = np.array(x_vals, dtype=float)\r\n        self.y_vals = np.array(y_vals, dtype=float)\r\n        self.n = len(x_vals) - 1\r\n        self._coeffs = None\r\n        self._fit()\r\n\r\n    def _fit(self):\r\n        \"\"\"求解三次样条系数。\"\"\"\r\n        n \n... (truncated)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783379980776}}
