{"type":"message","id":"03baaacb","parentId":"2837b0de","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:23:18.650Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我犯了一个错误。来看一下原来的代码：\n\n```\n        # 计算候选增益\n        cr = self._current_red + max(-step, min(step, int(g_sum / max(1, r_sum) * self._current_red) - self._current_red))\n        cb = self._current_blue + max(-step, min(step, int(g_sum / max(1, b_sum) * self._current_blue) - self._current_blue))\n        cr = max(1, min(255, cr))\n        cb = max(1, min(255, cb))\n```\n\n这段代码在计算候选增益时使用了 `step` 变量。如果我把 `actual` 的计算移到前面，那么需要确保 `r_sum`, `g_sum`, `b_sum` 已经计算出来。\n\n但是 `_rgb_stats 返回字典包含 r_sum, g_sum, b_sum`，这些已经在这里计算了。所以把 `actual` 的计算移到前面是安全的。\n\n但是我发现一个问题：原来的代码中，精调阶段的处理逻辑是：\n\n```python\n        # 精调阶段处理\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            self._fine_steps += 1\n            if self._no_improve >= 3 or self._fine_steps >= 10:\n                ...\n```\n\n然后我用新的逻辑替换了这一块。\n\n但是还有一个问题：在我的新代码中，`self._stage_steps[2]` 在精调阶段处理中被更新了。但是这个更新是在这一步的 RETURN 之前的。\n\n让我重新思考一下精调阶段的逻辑。\n\n精调阶段应该使用根据当前场景动态调整的步长。不同场景下，步长应该有所变化：高场景差异时使用更大步长，精准微调时使用小步长。通过实时计算场景差异并调整步长，可以提高搜索效率和精度。\n\n具体实现是在每一轮搜索前，根据当前场景参数调整步长，并在返回不同场景时通知精调模式变化。这种方法可以更好地适应不同拍摄条件下的白平衡搜索需求。\n\n关键修改包括在初始化时增加新字段记录精调模式，并完善精调阶段处理逻辑，根据不同场景自动切换步长策略。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a795d6081eba4112a87130d4","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":140,"offset":135,"path":"astrohub/src/controlpanel/whitebalance.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":64094,"output":490,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64584,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783380154387,"responseId":"cht000d7d5b@dx19f39bdb5e829c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9db0b5f9","parentId":"03baaacb","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:23:18.663Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a795d6081eba4112a87130d4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            new_stage = [\"medium\", \"fine\"][self._stage - 1]\r\n            return {\r\n                \"action\": \"continue\",\r\n                \"stage\": new_stage,\r\n                \"step_size\": self._stage_steps[self._stage],\r\n                \"red_gain\": self._current_red, \"blue_gain\": self._current_blue,\r\n                \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\r\n                \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\r\n                \"message\": f\"进入{'中等' if self._stage == 1 else '精细'}调校 (step=±{self._stage_steps[self._stage]})\"\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        # 精调阶段处理：3档动态步进\r\n        if self._stage == 2:\r\n            # 根据 delta 选择步长\r\n            if actual >= 200:\r\n                step = 5\r\n                self._fine_step_mode = 5\r\n            elif actual >= 10:\r\n                step = 2\r\n                self._fine_step_mode = 2\r\n            else:\r\n                step = 1\r\n                self._fine_step_mode = 1\r\n                self._fine_steps += 1\r\n                if self._fine_steps >= 30:\r\n                    rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\r\n                    self._current_red = self._best_red\r\n                    self._current_blue = self._best_blue\r\n                    return {\r\n                        \"action\": \"stop\",\r\n                        \"stage\": \"done\",\r\n                        \"step_size\": 0,\r\n                        \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\r\n                        \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\r\n                        \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\r\n                        \"message\": f\"白平衡完成(1步精调{self._fine_steps}次上限) {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\r\n                    }\r\n            # 5步和2步模式：无次数限制，继续搜索\r\n            # 更新 stage_steps[2] 为当前动态步长\r\n            self._stage_steps[2] = step\r\n\r\n        # 应用新增益\r\n        self._current_red = new_red\r\n        self._current_blue = new_blue\r\n        return {\r\n            \"action\": \"continue\",\r\n            \"stage\": stage_name,\r\n            \"step_size\": step,\r\n            \"red_gain\": new_red, \"blue_gain\": new_blue,\r\n            \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\r\n            \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\r\n            \"message\": f\"{'粗' if self._stage == 0 else '中' if self._stage == 1 else '精'}调 {direction} (±{step})\"\r\n        }\r\n\r\n\r\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n# 执行层：协调设备操作\r\n# ─────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\nclass WhiteBalanceSearcher:\r\n    \"\"\"白平衡搜索执行器\r\n    \r\n    负责：\r\n    - 切换手动白平衡模式\r\n    - 读取当前增益\r\n    - 截取框选区域\r\n    - 调用IterativeWB.step()\r\n    - 应用增益到设备\r\n    - 切换锁定白平衡模式\r\n    - 验证结果\r\n    - 产生SSE事件\r\n    \r\n    不做任何算法决策，只执行。\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    \r\n    def __init__(self, mgr, device_ip, client, x, y, w, h, capture_func, cleanup_func, mac_clean=\"\"):\r\n        self.mgr = mgr\r\n        self.device_ip = device_ip\r\n        self.client = client\r\n        self.x = x\r\n        self.y = y\r\n        self.w = w\r\n        self.h = h\r\n        self._capture_func = capture_func\r\n        self._cleanup_func = cleanup_func\r\n        self._interrupted = False  # v8.41: 中断标志\r\n        self._mac_clean = mac_clean  # v8.47: 用于保存设置\r\n    \r\n    def _set_wb_mode(self, mode: str):\r\n        \"\"\"设置白平衡模式: manual/locked\"\"\"\r\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<WhiteBalance version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n<WhiteBalanceStyle>{mode}</WhiteBalanceStyle>\r\n</WhiteBalance>'''\r\n        resp = self.client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\", xml)\r\n        return resp.status_code == 200\r\n    \r\n    def _set_wb_gains(self, red: int, blue: int):\r\n        \"\"\"设置白平衡增益\"\"\"\r\n        xml = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<WhiteBalance version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n<WhiteBalanceStyle>manual</WhiteBalanceStyle>\r\n<WhiteBalanceRed>{red}</WhiteBalanceRed>\r\n<WhiteBalanceBlue>{blue}</WhiteBalanceBlue>\r\n</WhiteBalance>'''\r\n        resp = self.client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\", xml)\r\n        return resp.status_code == 200\r\n    \r\n    def _read_current_gains(self):\r\n        \"\"\"读取当前白平衡增益\"\"\"\r\n        try:\r\n            resp = self.client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\")\r\n            if resp.status_code == 200:\r\n                # 解析XML\r\n                import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n                root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n                red, blue = 100, 100\r\n                for elem in root.iter():\r\n                    tag = elem.tag.split('}')[-1] if '}' in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n                    if tag in (\"WhiteBalanceRed\", \"whiteBalanceRed\"):\r\n                        red = int(elem.text)\r\n                    elif tag in (\"WhiteBalanceBlue\", \"whiteBalanceBlue\"):\r\n                        blue = int(elem.text)\r\n                return red, blue\r\n        except:\r\n            pass\r\n        return 100, 100\r\n    \r\n    def _capture(self):\r\n        \"\"\"截取框选区域\"\"\"\r\n        bgr, crop_path, info = self._capture_func(\r\n            self.client, self.mgr, self.device_ip, \"WB\",\r\n            self.x, self.y, self.w, self.h\r\n        )\r\n        return bgr, info\r\n    \r\n    def _interrupt(self):\r\n        \"\"\"v8.41: 中断白平衡搜索\"\"\"\r\n        self._interrupted = True\r\n    \r\n\n[97 more lines in file. Use offset=275 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783380198663}}
{"type":"message","id":"f795629d","parentId":"9db0b5f9","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:23:39.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看到问题了！精调阶段的处理块在候选增益计算之后运行，但它修改了 `step` 变量。问题是：\n\n1. 上方动态选择了 step（比如5）\n2. 候选增益用 step=5 计算\n3. 精调处理块又重新计算 step（可能还是5，但也可能不同）\n4. 最后返回的 step_size 用的是精调块里的 step\n\n实际上这里有个更深层的问题：精调处理块中的 `step` 变量和上方动态选择的 `step` 是同一个变量。但因为精调块重新计算了 step，所以最终的 step 值取决于精调块。\n\n不过仔细看，上方动态选择 step 时也计算了 `actual`，然后精调块又计算了一遍。但实际上我在修复4中已经把上方的 `actual` 计算移到了前面，精调块里的 `actual` 就不需要重新计算了。\n\n让我重新审视代码逻辑：\n\n1. 上方：计算 actual → 根据 actual 动态选择 step（stage 2）\n2. 用 step 计算候选增益\n3. 选最优候选\n4. `actual` 已在上方计算（注释掉了重复）\n5. 更新 best\n6. 阶段升级检查\n7. 精调处理块：重新根据 actual 选择 step → 但这里的 step 变量是新的\n\n等等，这里有个逻辑问题。精调块中的 step 会覆盖上方计算的 step。但候选增益已经用上方的 step 计算完了。所以精调块里的 step 只影响返回的 `step_size` 字段，不影响实际的候选增益计算。\n\n这其实不对。应该是：每一步都用当前 delta 选择步长，然后基于这个步长计算候选增益。我需要删除精调块中的重复逻辑。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8586d45fca3d42639e9a01ba","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Fix whitebalance.py: remove duplicate step logic in fine block\"\"\"\n\npath = r\"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py\"\nwith open(path, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# The fine block has duplicate step selection. \n# The step is already selected at the top of step() method.\n# The fine block should only handle the 1-step counter and stop condition.\n\nold_fine_block = \"\"\"        # 精调阶段处理：3档动态步进\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            # 根据 delta 选择步长\n            if actual >= 200:\n                step = 5\n                self._fine_step_mode = 5\n            elif actual >= 10:\n                step = 2\n                self._fine_step_mode = 2\n            else:\n                step = 1\n                self._fine_step_mode = 1\n                self._fine_steps += 1\n                if self._fine_steps >= 30:\n                    rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\n                    self._current_red = self._best_red\n                    self._current_blue = self._best_blue\n                    return {\n                        \"action\": \"stop\",\n                        \"stage\": \"done\",\n                        \"step_size\": 0,\n                        \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\n                        \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                        \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                        \"message\": f\"白平衡完成(1步精调{self._fine_steps}次上限) {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\n                    }\n            # 5步和2步模式：无次数限制，继续搜索\n            # 更新 stage_steps[2] 为当前动态步长\n            self._stage_steps[2] = step\"\"\"\n\nnew_fine_block = \"\"\"        # 精调阶段处理：1步模式计数器\n        if self._stage == 2 and step == 1:\n            self._fine_step_mode = 1\n            self._fine_steps += 1\n            if self._fine_steps >= 30:\n                rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\n                self._current_red = self._best_red\n                self._current_blue = self._best_blue\n                return {\n                    \"action\": \"stop\",\n                    \"stage\": \"done\",\n                    \"step_size\": 0,\n                    \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\n                    \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                    \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                    \"message\": f\"白平衡完成(1步精调{self._fine_steps}次上限) {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\n                }\n        elif self._stage == 2 and step > 1:\n            self._fine_step_mode = step\"\"\"\n\nif old_fine_block not in content:\n    print(\"ERROR: old fine block not found\")\n    exit(1)\n\ncontent = content.replace(old_fine_block, new_fine_block)\n\nwith open(path, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n    f.write(content)\n\nprint(\"OK: fine block cleaned up\")\n","path":"astrohub/_fix_wb2.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":65743,"output":1244,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66987,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783380198664,"responseId":"cht000d94d3@dx19f39be4bce29c2503"}}
