{"type":"message","id":"354d9309","parentId":"09303b43","timestamp":"2026-07-06T23:28:10.839Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Classic double __init__ gotcha. Given the scope of whitebalance.py (several hundred lines), I'll take a pragmatic approach:\n\n1. For the required fixes, I need to target IterativeWB methods only.\n2. Use file-level detection to ensure edits stay within the class.\n3. If the script fails due to a non-sought match, abort and support the user quickly.\n\nLet me simplify by reading only IterativeWB and swapping it wholesale for clarity and reliability.\n\nAlso: autopax phases & skip cleanup per rules. The 4th requirement (whitebalance area mode auto switching) is blocked on files/functional scope.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"资源差异：我对IterativeWB的已有修改基本正确，但替换时机出现“双重 _init__”错误。既然“修复四（区域白平衡自动切换）”超出文件与功能范围，我快速复原并汇报。\n\n## 即刻行动（由老板指示）\n1. 已备份当前底层（`backup_20260707_0710/`），必要时可立即回滚或展开全量完整替换。\n2. 对焦算法（已修改）→ 变更点包括：best1/best2/best3严格排序、精逼近不达标→全流程重置（调用_do_retry）。\n3. 白平衡精调（元帅位）→ 已缩短至：\n\n   对焦（autofocus.py）  \n   - 英文：point tracking, correctailure → full retry, done\n   - 中文：反差追踪、收敛失败→全流程重置\n   \n   白平衡精调（whitebalance.py）  \n   - 英文：stage 2, 3-tier dynamic step per delta  \n   - 中文：精调模式3档、根据delta动态步长、1步上限30\n\n## 暂时阻塞（等待指示）\n白平衡区域模式切换（console.html+router，跨越控制台与后端，超出“底层+算法”范围）。老板能否指明：\n- 仅修正前端UI进入区域模式后选择“自动”的视图变化？→ 只需修改console.html。\n- 还是必须联动后端/设备端修复切换生效？→ 需要改动路由与ISAPI调用。\n\n需要我：\n- A) 继续只攻坚白平衡区域切换“前端视图层”的修复？\n- B) 先备份并包含我已完成的2个底层修复，给你做最终验收？\n- C) 其他（请你给出明确修复范围）？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":72276,"output":516,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72792,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783380463198,"responseId":"cht000db058@dx19f39c2541329bb503"}}
