{"type":"message","id":"f772bba2","parentId":"703dcbdf","timestamp":"2026-07-07T07:49:25.208Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me use edit with the exact content:\n\nCurrent (line 57-59):\n```python\n        step = self._stage_steps[self._stage]\n\n        # 计算候选增益\n```\n\nNew (动态步长选择 + actual提前计算 + 统一的注释):\n```python\n        # 计算当前delta（用于精调阶段动态步长）\n        actual = abs(r_sum / max(1, g_sum) - 1.0) + abs(b_sum / max(1, g_sum) - 1.0)\n\n        # 精调阶段：根据delta动态选择步长\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            if actual >= 200:\n                step = 5\n            elif actual >= 10:\n                step = 2\n            else:\n                step = 1\n        else:\n            step = self._stage_steps[self._stage]\n\n        # 计算候选增益\n```\n\nThen replace the fine stage block.","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我重新读取了文件内容。现在用精确的文字匹配进行替换。3个位置：\n\n**位置1**：line 57-59 的 step = self._stage_steps[...] → 动态步长选择\n\n**位置2**：精调阶段处理块（line 107-138）→ 修改为只处理1步计数器"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a34a12b96d104a87a549ca3d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":5,"offset":59,"path":"astrohub/src/controlpanel/whitebalance.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":80676,"output":308,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80984,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783410486524,"responseId":"cht000df3a7@dx19f3b8cdac529c2503"}}
