{"type":"message","id":"6e69d84e","parentId":"7e27c620","timestamp":"2026-07-07T07:58:14.107Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板要求：\n\n1. **白平衡精调**：恢复 `_no_improve >= 3` 和 `_fine_steps >= 10` 的逻辑，只保留步进5和步进2的调整\n   - 意思是：精调阶段还是用原来的停止条件（_no_improve >= 3 或 _fine_steps >= 10）\n   - 但步长改为动态：delta >= 200 → 5步，10 <= delta < 200 → 2步，delta < 10 → 1步\n   - 不需要1步上限30次的逻辑了\n\n2. **主控台白平衡下拉菜单**：点击\"局部\"后再点回\"自动\"，没有生效。要检查根因，并且检查其他下拉选项是否也有同样问题。\n\n先处理第1点：恢复原来的停止条件，但保留动态步长。\n\n再处理第2点：排查 onWbModeChange 和 setWhiteBalanceMode 的调用链。\n\n让我先读取当前 whitebalance.py 的状态，确认之前的修改情况。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"明白，两个任务：\n\n1. 白平衡：恢复 `_no_improve >= 3` / `_fine_steps >= 10` 停止条件，只加步进5和步进2的动态调整\n2. 主控台白平衡下拉菜单：局部→自动不生效，排查根因并修复\n\n先读取当前 whitebalance.py 的修改状态，再排查下拉菜单问题。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9619b7f9f34f423f81e88c62","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":120,"offset":53,"path":"astrohub/src/controlpanel/whitebalance.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":84672,"output":333,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85005,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783411052433,"responseId":"cht000d5f65@dx19f3b9577c329bb503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b183b7bc","parentId":"6e69d84e","timestamp":"2026-07-07T07:58:14.120Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9619b7f9f34f423f81e88c62","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    def step(self, bgr) -> dict:\r\n        \"\"\"输入BGR图像，返回下一步动作\"\"\"\r\n        stats = _rgb_stats(bgr)\r\n        n = stats[\"n\"]\r\n        r_sum, g_sum, b_sum = stats[\"r_sum\"], stats[\"g_sum\"], stats[\"b_sum\"]\r\n\r\n        self._step_count += 1\r\n        self._stage_step_count += 1\r\n        # 计算当前delta（用于精调阶段动态步长）\r\n        actual = abs(r_sum / max(1, g_sum) - 1.0) + abs(b_sum / max(1, g_sum) - 1.0)\r\n\r\n        # 精调阶段：根据delta动态选择步长\r\n        if self._stage == 2:\r\n            if actual >= 200:\r\n                step = 5\r\n            elif actual >= 10:\r\n                step = 2\r\n            else:\r\n                step = 1\r\n        else:\r\n            step = self._stage_steps[self._stage]\r\n\r\n        # 计算候选增益\r\n        cr = self._current_red + max(-step, min(step, int(g_sum / max(1, r_sum) * self._current_red) - self._current_red))\r\n        cb = self._current_blue + max(-step, min(step, int(g_sum / max(1, b_sum) * self._current_blue) - self._current_blue))\r\n        cr = max(1, min(255, cr))\r\n        cb = max(1, min(255, cb))\r\n\r\n        # 候选列表 (- stage 2: R/B独立调整)\r\n        if self._stage == 2:\r\n            # 精调阶段：全部R/B独立，无\"both\"候选\r\n            candidates = [(cr, self._current_blue, \"red\"), (self._current_red, cb, \"blue\")]\r\n        else:\r\n            candidates = [(cr, cb, \"both\"), (cr, self._current_blue, \"red\"), (self._current_red, cb, \"blue\")]\r\n\r\n        # 选最优候选\r\n        best_cand = None\r\n        best_d = 999.0\r\n        for r, b, label in candidates:\r\n            d = self._eval(r_sum, g_sum, b_sum, r, b)\r\n            if d < best_d:\r\n                best_d = d\r\n                best_cand = (r, b, label)\r\n\r\n        new_red, new_blue, direction = best_cand\r\n        new_red = int(new_red)\r\n        new_blue = int(new_blue)\r\n\r\n        # actual 已在上方计算\r\n\r\n        # 更新best\r\n        prev_best = self._best_delta\r\n        if actual < self._best_delta:\r\n            self._best_delta = actual\r\n            self._best_red = self._current_red\r\n            self._best_blue = self._current_blue\r\n            self._best_step = self._step_count\r\n\r\n        # 无改善计数\r\n        tolerance = self._tolerances[self._stage]\r\n        if actual >= prev_best * tolerance:\r\n            self._no_improve += 1\r\n        else:\r\n            self._no_improve = 0\r\n\r\n        stage_name = [\"coarse\", \"medium\", \"fine\"][self._stage]\r\n        min_steps = self._stage_min[self._stage]\r\n\r\n        # 阶段升级\r\n        if self._stage < 2 and self._stage_step_count >= min_steps and self._no_improve >= 2:\r\n            self._stage += 1\r\n            self._stage_step_count = 0\r\n            self._no_improve = 0\r\n            # 进入精调时重置best追踪，避免粗调阶段的best覆盖精调结果\r\n            if self._stage == 2:\r\n                self._best_delta = 999.0\r\n                self._best_red = self._current_red\r\n                self._best_blue = self._current_blue\r\n                self._best_step = self._step_count\r\n            new_stage = [\"medium\", \"fine\"][self._stage - 1]\r\n            return {\r\n                \"action\": \"continue\",\r\n                \"stage\": new_stage,\r\n                \"step_size\": self._stage_steps[self._stage],\r\n                \"red_gain\": self._current_red, \"blue_gain\": self._current_blue,\r\n                \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\r\n                \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\r\n                \"message\": f\"进入{'中等' if self._stage == 1 else '精细'}调校 (step=±{self._stage_steps[self._stage]})\"\r\n            }\r\n\r\n        # 精调阶段：1步模式计数器（上限30）\r\n        if self._stage == 2 and step == 1:\r\n            self._fine_steps += 1\r\n            if self._fine_steps >= 30:\r\n                rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\r\n                self._current_red = self._best_red\r\n                self._current_blue = self._best_blue\r\n                return {\r\n                    \"action\": \"stop\",\r\n                    \"stage\": \"done\",\r\n                    \"step_size\": 0,\r\n                    \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\r\n                    \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\r\n                    \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\r\n                    \"message\": f\"白平衡完成(1步精调{self._fine_steps}次上限) {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\r\n                }\r\n\r\n        # 应用新增益\r\n        self._current_red = new_red\r\n        self._current_blue = new_blue\r\n        return {\r\n            \"action\": \"continue\",\r\n            \"stage\": stage_name,\r\n            \"step_size\": step,\r\n            \"red_gain\": new_red, \"blue_gain\": new_blue,\r\n            \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\r\n            \"delta\": round(actual, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\r\n            \"message\": f\"{'粗' if self._stage == 0 else '中' if self._stage == 1 else '精'}调 {direction} (±{step})\"\r\n        }\r\n\r\n\n[183 more lines in file. Use offset=173 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783411094120}}
{"type":"message","id":"df5c6f3e","parentId":"b183b7bc","timestamp":"2026-07-07T07:59:40.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前代码：\n- Line 54-65：动态步进逻辑（delta>=200→5步，10<=delta<200→2步，delta<10→1步）\n- Line 177-190：精调阶段的处理，只有 \"if self._stage == 2 and step == 1:\" 这段，返回上限30次的停止逻辑\n\n老板要求：\n- 恢复 `_no_improve >= 3` / `_fine_steps >= 10` 的逻辑\n- 只保留步进5和步进2的调整\n\n也就是说：\n1. 精调阶段的步长只能是什么模式？\n   - delta >= 200 → step = 5\n   - 10 <= delta < 200 → step = 2\n   - delta < 10 → step = 1 ?? 不，老板说\"只保留步进5和步进2的调整\"，意味着不需要1步模式？\n\n等等，我再理解一下。老板说：\n\"1. 恢复_no_improve >= 3、_fine_steps >= 10的逻辑，只保留步进5和步进2的调整\"\n\n可能的解读：\n1. 恢复 stop 条件：_no_improve >= 3 或 _fine_steps >= 10\n2. 步进调整逻辑：只在精调阶段使用步进5和步进2，不再有1步模式？\n\n但这样的话，怎么收敛到极致呢？\n\n或者理解为：\n1. 恢复 stop 条件：_no_improve >= 3 或 _fine_steps >= 10\n\n\n2. 添加条件逻辑：只有在本地或中等步长下才继续精调，超过10步则停止\n\n我认为这种方法更合理：在本地和中等步长阶段灵活调整，确保算法不会无限迭代。当达到10步仍未优化时，果断结束搜索过程。\n\n对于1步调整，可能需要单独设计匹配机制，确保算法的精准性和效率。接下来需要仔细检查前端代码逻辑。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"我看到问题了。当前代码中精调阶段只有 1步模式计数器（上限30）。老板要求恢复原来的 stop 条件 `_no_improve >= 3` 和 `_fine_steps >= 10`，但在精调阶段只使用步进5和2。\n\n让我先读取 console.html 的完整 white balance 逻辑，找出主控台下拉菜单的问题根因："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_218b4f332735421cbd3240b0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub && Select-String -Path src\\web\\includes\\console.html -Pattern \"function setWhiteBalanceMode|function onWbModeChange|loadWhiteBalance\" -AllMatches | Select-Object LineNumber, Line"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":86770,"output":563,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":87333,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783411094122,"responseId":"cht000dedd4@dx19f3b963fa829c2503"}}
