{"type":"message","id":"66581f52","parentId":"23c3f4c1","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:00:04.240Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b30926fd472042209bcdda98","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function setWhiteBalanceMode(mode) {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: mode })\r\n        .then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success) {\r\n                showToast('success', '白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'));\r\n                if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'), 'success');\r\n            }\r\n        });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 设置白平衡增益 R/B\r\nfunction setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value) {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n\r\n    // 更新显示\r\n    if (channel === 'red') {\r\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\r\n    } else {\r\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    var key = channel === 'red' ? 'red_gain' : 'blue_gain';\r\n    var label = channel === 'red' ? 'R (红增益)' : 'B (蓝增益)';\r\n\r\n    // v6.56: 只发送增益值,不发送模式(模式已通过下拉菜单切换)\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { [key]: parseInt(value) })\r\n        .then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success) {\r\n                showToast('success', label + ': ' + value);\r\n                if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('白平衡' + label + ': ' + value, 'success');\r\n            }\r\n        });\r\n}\r\n\r\n\n[508 more lines in file. Use offset=1568 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783411204240}}
{"type":"message","id":"afb853be","parentId":"66581f52","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:04:35.333Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我看到了问题的关键：\n\n1. `onWbModeChange(mode)` (line 1251)：\n   ```javascript\n   function onWbModeChange(mode) {\n       var manualControls = document.getElementById('wbManualControls');\n       var localControls = document.getElementById('wbLocalControls');\n       var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\n       var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\n\n       if (mode === 'manual') {\n           // 显示手动控件，切换到手动模式\n           setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\n       } else if (mode === 'local') {\n           // 隐藏手动控件，显示局部控件，切换到手动模式\n           manualControls.style.display = 'none';\n           localControls.style.display = 'block';\n           if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\n           if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\n           setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\n       } else {\n           // 自动模式\n           manualControls.style.display = 'none';\n           localControls.style.display = 'none';\n           if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\n           if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\n           setWhiteBalanceMode('auto');\n       }\n   }\n   ```\n\n2. `setWhiteBalanceMode(mode)` (line 1528)：\n   ```javascript\n   function setWhiteBalanceMode(mode) {\n       var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n       if (!dev) return;\n\n       apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: mode })\n           .then(function(r) {\n               if (r && r.success) {\n                   showToast('success', '白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'));\n                   if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'), 'success');\n               }\n           });\n   }\n   ```\n\n我注意到这段代码处理白平衡模式的切换逻辑。当选择不同的白平衡模式时，代码会执行一系列操作：隐藏或显示特定的控件，更新控件状态，并通过API调用设置设备白平衡模式。关键点是确保只在存在连接设备时执行操作，并通过后端API进行模式切换。 检查 `wbMode` 的 HTML 结构，发现不同位置存在重复的 'auto' 选项。追踪 HTML 内容将揭示下拉菜单的完整配置。\n\n通过搜索定位到关键区域：\n- 头部缓存定义了 wbMode\n- 局部控制区域和主控台都有同样的选项\n\n初步分析暗示可能存在重复的 'auto' 选项效果。需要进一步验证具体变更是否真的生效。\n\n检查 `onWbModeChange` 和 `setWhiteBalanceMode` 的实现细节，发现调用流程看起来正常。关键在于 `apiPost` 是否真正触发后端接口变化。\n\n路由端点接受 mode 参数，从 ISAPI 读取当前状态，并使用传入的新模式。整体交互机制似乎设计合理。\n\n需要进一步排查调用链路中的潜在问题，特别是确认白平衡模式是否按预期切换。\n\n核心疑点在于区域模式下是否真正生效，需要验证后端是否能正确处理和应用自动模式设置。\n\n目前发现 `onWbModeChange` 中对局部模式的处理与白平衡模式存在分离，可能意味着用户操作流程与实际模式切换不同步。需要进一步检查模式切换的具体实现逻辑。\n\n前端 HTML 的 `wbMode` select 元素似乎存在，但客户端代码节点检查可能会影响设置过程。\n\n具体问题在于局部模式下控件状态和模式处理的不一致性。\n\n需要重新设计 `onWbModeChange` 逻辑，确保在不同模式下（局部、手动、自动）正确管理显隐和设备状态切换。核心是精细控制客户端 UI 和后端白平衡模式。\n\n我将全面排查相关代码，包括图表的控件管理、区域模式、捕获功能、状态重置等，确保系统表现精确。对于白平衡模式切换，需要检查多个端的实现细节，包括 HTML 渲染、前端逻辑、后端路由和 ISAPI 调用。重点是定位影响模式切换的具体环节。\n\n接下来我将系统性地检查图表代码，追踪国际化 messages 和曲线谱相关的 whitebalance 逻辑。同时，我还将审查 console.html 中的历史回滚和参数重置功能，确保模式切换的流畅性和准确性。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，我理解了。让我重新组织修复：\n\n## 任务审查\n\n**1. 白平衡精调**：恢复 `_no_improve >= 3`/`_fine_steps >= 10` 停止条件，只保留步进5和2的动态调整\n**2. 主控台白平衡下拉菜单**：\"局部\"→\"自动\"不生效，需要排查并修复，同时检查其他下拉选项是否也有同样问题\n\n先用一个脚本完整处理白平衡的问题，再排查下拉菜单问题。先从白平衡开始。\n\n让我先完整读取白平衡代码，然后用一个脚本把手动版本中的精调条件恢复（恢复 `_no_improve >= 3` 和 `_fine_steps >= 10`），同时保留动态步进（5步和2步）。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8ccc311dbbd24b5db189f1e5","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\"\"\"Fix whitebalance.py: 恢复精调停止条件，只保留步进5和2的动态调整\"\"\"\n\npath = r\"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py\"\n\nwith open(path, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# ── 修改1: 把动态步进的delta<10改为delta<10时就不进入精调阶段（保持step=1） ──\nold1 = \"\"\"        # 精调阶段：根据delta动态选择步长\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            if actual >= 200:\n                step = 5\n            elif actual >= 10:\n                step = 2\n            else:\n                step = 1\n        else:\n            step = self._stage_steps[self._stage]\"\"\"\n\nnew1 = \"\"\"        # 精调阶段：根据delta动态选择步长（delta<10时保持step=1）\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            if actual >= 200:\n                step = 5\n            elif actual >= 10:\n                step = 2\n        else:\n            step = self._stage_steps[self._stage]\"\"\"\n\nif old1 not in content:\n    print(\"ERROR: old1 not found\")\n    exit(1)\ncontent = content.replace(old1, new1)\nprint(\"OK: 1/2 - fine stage step adjustment updated\")\n\n# ── 修改2: 替换精调阶段处理块，恢复 `_no_improve >= 3` 和 `_fine_steps >= 10` 停止条件 ──\nold2 = \"\"\"        # 精调阶段：1步模式计数器（上限30）\n        if self._stage == 2 and step == 1:\n            self._fine_steps += 1\n            if self._fine_steps >= 30:\n                rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\n                self._current_red = self._best_red\n                self._current_blue = self._best_blue\n                return {\n                    \"action\": \"stop\",\n                    \"stage\": \"done\",\n                    \"step_size\": 0,\n                    \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\n                    \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                    \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                    \"message\": f\"白平衡完成(1步精调{self._fine_steps}次上限) {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\n                }\n\n        # 应用新增益\"\"\"\n\nnew2 = \"\"\"        # 精调阶段：恢复 `_no_improve >= 3` 和 `_fine_steps >= 10` 停止条件\n        if self._stage == 2:\n            self._fine_steps += 1\n            if self._no_improve >= 3 or self._fine_steps >= 10:\n                rollback = (self._best_red != self._current_red or self._best_blue != self._current_blue)\n                self._current_red = self._best_red\n                self._current_blue = self._best_blue\n                return {\n                    \"action\": \"stop\",\n                    \"stage\": \"done\",\n                    \"step_size\": 0,\n                    \"red_gain\": self._best_red, \"blue_gain\": self._best_blue,\n                    \"r_avg\": round(stats[\"r_avg\"], 1), \"g_avg\": round(stats[\"g_avg\"], 1), \"b_avg\": round(stats[\"b_avg\"], 1),\n                    \"delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"best_delta\": round(self._best_delta, 4), \"pixels\": n,\n                    \"message\": f\"白平衡完成 {'(回滚至最佳)' if rollback else '(已达最佳)'} 第{self._best_step}步\"\n                }\n\n        # 应用新增益\"\"\"\n\nif old2 not in content:\n    print(\"ERROR: old2 not found\")\n    exit(1)\ncontent = content.replace(old2, new2)\nprint(\"OK: 2/2 - fine stage stop condition restored\")\n\nwith open(path, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n    f.write(content)\n\nprint(\"DONE: whitebalance.py restored to manual version with dynamic step adjustment\")\n","path":"astrohub/_fix_wb_v837.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":87865,"output":2093,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89958,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783411204241,"responseId":"cht000da72c@dx19f3b98d79d2872503"}}
