{"type":"message","id":"c7584d01","parentId":"53d9414c","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:07:22.666Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板非常生气了！他说：\n1. \"你做什么啊！！！！\" - 极度不满\n2. 完全回滚 whitebalance.py\n3. \"改的乱七八糟的！\" - 我改坏了\n4. 现在的优先任务是：修复下拉菜单\n5. 修复完成后，回滚 whitebalance.py 给老板汇报\n\n我现在需要：\n1. **立即**回滚 whitebalance.py 到备份版本\n2. 然后排查下拉菜单问题\n3. 修复下拉菜单问题\n4. 回滚 whitebalance.py\n5. 给老板汇报\n\n不要再做任何关于 whitebalance.py 其他修改了！先把白平衡回滚，然后专心处理下拉菜单问题。\n\n让我先回滚 whitebalance.py，然后读取下拉菜单的完整逻辑，找出问题根源。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"老板，我立即回滚！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0923509a231947508236ec33","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Copy-Item -Force C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\backup_20260707_0710\\whitebalance.py.bak C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\agents\\dev-factory\\astrohub\\src\\controlpanel\\whitebalance.py; echo ROLLED_BACK"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":90165,"output":255,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90420,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783411607892,"responseId":"cht000dae9d@dx19f3b9d925d29c2503"}}
