{"type":"message","id":"4d795606","parentId":"7ff98d13","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:16:26.224Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4e2fa5f456cc481689eac32b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function setWhiteBalanceMode(mode) {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance', { mode: mode })\r\n        .then(function(r) {\r\n            if (r && r.success) {\r\n                showToast('success', '白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'));\r\n                if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('白平衡: ' + (mode === 'auto' ? '自动' : '手动'), 'success');\r\n            }\r\n        });\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 设置白平衡增益 R/B\r\nfunction setWhiteBalanceGain(channel, value) {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n\r\n    // 更新显示\r\n    if (channel === 'red') {\r\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\r\n    } else {\r\n        var el = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n        if (el) el.textContent = value;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    var key = channel === 'red' ? 'red_gain' : 'blue_gain';\r\n    var label = channel === 'red' ? 'R (红增益)' : 'B (蓝增益)';\r\n\r\n\n[518 more lines in file. Use offset=1558 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783412186224}}
{"type":"message","id":"abcd7f88","parentId":"4d795606","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:17:53.489Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到了白平衡相关的代码：\n\n1. `onWbModeChange(mode)` - 处理下拉菜单切换\n2. `setWhiteBalanceMode(mode)` - 调用后端 API\n\n问题：\n- 点击\"局部\"后，会隐藏 manualControls，显示 localControls\n- 然后调用 `setWhiteBalanceMode('manual')`\n- 再点击回\"自动\"后，`onWbModeChange('auto')` 被调用，但 `loadWhiteBalance` 没有被触发\n\n让我检查 `loadWhiteBalance` 的逻辑，看看它是如何设置下拉菜单的。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_73119e44f1ca44eb98feb09f","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":40,"offset":1002,"path":"astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":91532,"output":161,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91693,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783412186226,"responseId":"cht000d8ae6@dx19f3ba741162871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6925bf97","parentId":"abcd7f88","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:17:53.503Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_73119e44f1ca44eb98feb09f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"function loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp) {\r\n    apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + deviceIp + '/image/whitebalance').then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success && r.data) {\r\n            var wb = r.data;\r\n            deviceImageParams.whiteBalance = wb;\r\n\r\n            var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\r\n            if (wbModeSelect) {\r\n                // 根据设备返回的模式设置下拉菜单\r\n                if (wb.mode === 'manual') {\r\n                    wbModeSelect.value = 'manual';\r\n                } else {\r\n                    wbModeSelect.value = 'auto';\r\n                }\r\n                // 触发显示/隐藏逻辑\r\n                onWbModeChange(wbModeSelect.value);\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            // 更新 R/B 滑动条\r\n            var wbRed = document.getElementById('wbRed');\r\n            var wbBlue = document.getElementById('wbBlue');\r\n            var wbRedVal = document.getElementById('wbRedVal');\r\n            var wbBlueVal = document.getElementById('wbBlueVal');\r\n\r\n            if (wbRed && wb.red_gain !== undefined) {\r\n                wbRed.value = wb.red_gain;\r\n                if (wbRedVal) wbRedVal.textContent = wb.red_gain;\r\n            }\r\n            if (wbBlue && wb.blue_gain !== undefined) {\r\n                wbBlue.value = wb.blue_gain;\r\n                if (wbBlueVal) wbBlueVal.textContent = wb.blue_gain;\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            // 设置范围\r\n            if (wb.min !== undefined && wb.max !== undefined) {\r\n                if (wbRed) { wbRed.min = wb.min; wbRed.max = wb.max; }\r\n                if (wbBlue) { wbBlue.min = wb.min; wbBlue.max = wb.max; }\r\n            }\r\n\r\n            // 只有手动模式时 R/B 滑动条才可用\r\n\n[1034 more lines in file. Use offset=1042 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783412273503}}
