{"type":"message","id":"d286aaac","parentId":"cd971308","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:18:27.240Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在看后端 `set_whitebalance` 端点："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_36cc407e58fd48178e49e856","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":65,"offset":2933,"path":"astrohub/src/api/router.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":92014,"output":44,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92058,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783412291448,"responseId":"cht000db004@dx19f3ba822af29c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9769545f","parentId":"d286aaac","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:18:27.255Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_36cc407e58fd48178e49e856","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"@api_router.post(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/whitebalance\", summary=\"设置白平衡\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\nasync def set_whitebalance(device_id: str, data: dict) -> dict:\r\n    \"\"\"设置白平衡参数(模式或R/B增益)。\"\"\"\r\n    import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n    mgr: PTZDeviceController | None = _managers.get(\"ptz_controller\")\r\n    if not mgr:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": \"PTZDeviceController未初始化\"}\r\n\r\n    target_ip = _resolve_device_id_to_ip(mgr, device_id)\r\n    if not target_ip:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"无法解析设备标识: {device_id}\"}\r\n\r\n    ctrl, err = mgr._get_controller(target_ip)\r\n    if err:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": err}\r\n\r\n    client = ctrl.client\r\n    try:\r\n        # 参数处理\r\n        mode_input = data.get(\"mode\")\r\n        red_input = data.get(\"red_gain\")\r\n        blue_input = data.get(\"blue_gain\")\r\n\r\n        # 获取当前值\r\n        resp = client.get(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\")\r\n        current_mode = \"auto\"\r\n        current_red = 100\r\n        current_blue = 80\r\n        if resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            import xml.etree.ElementTree as ET\r\n            root = ET.fromstring(resp.xml)\r\n            for elem in root.iter():\r\n                tag = elem.tag.split(\"}\")[-1] if \"}\" in elem.tag else elem.tag\r\n                if tag == \"WhiteBalanceStyle\":\r\n                    current_mode = (elem.text or \"auto\").lower()\r\n                elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceRed\":\r\n                    current_red = int(elem.text or 100)\r\n                elif tag == \"WhiteBalanceBlue\":\r\n                    current_blue = int(elem.text or 80)\r\n\r\n        # 使用传入值或当前值\r\n        mode_val = mode_input if mode_input else current_mode\r\n        red_val = red_input if red_input is not None else current_red\r\n        blue_val = blue_input if blue_input is not None else current_blue\r\n\r\n        # ISAPI 要求小写\r\n        mode_isapi = mode_val.lower() if mode_val else \"manual\"\r\n\r\n        xml_str = f'''<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\r\n<WhiteBalance version=\"2.0\" xmlns=\"http://www.hikvision.com/ver20/XMLSchema\">\r\n<WhiteBalanceStyle>{mode_isapi}</WhiteBalanceStyle>\r\n<WhiteBalanceRed>{red_val}</WhiteBalanceRed>\r\n<WhiteBalanceBlue>{blue_val}</WhiteBalanceBlue>\r\n</WhiteBalance>'''\r\n\r\n        put_resp = client.put(\"/Image/channels/1/whiteBalance\", xml_str)\r\n        if put_resp.status_code == 200:\r\n            log_info(\"image\", \"whitebalance\", {\"device\": device_id, \"mode\": mode_val, \"red\": red_val, \"blue\": blue_val})\r\n            return {\"success\": True, \"message\": \"白平衡已更新\", \"data\": {\"mode\": mode_val, \"red_gain\": red_val, \"blue_gain\": blue_val}}\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"更新失败: HTTP {put_resp.status_code}\"}\r\n    except Exception as e:\r\n        return {\"success\": False, \"message\": f\"设置白平衡异常: {e}\"}\r\n\r\n\r\n@api_router.get(\"/ptz/{device_id}/image/noisereduce\", summary=\"获取降噪设置\", tags=[\"Image\"])\r\n\n[1322 more lines in file. Use offset=2998 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783412307255}}
{"type":"message","id":"95454491","parentId":"9769545f","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:19:39.840Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到根因了。\n\n看后端 `set_whitebalance`：\n\n```python\nmode_val = mode_input if mode_input else current_mode\n```\n\n问题在这行：`if mode_input` — 当 `mode_input = \"auto\"` 时，Python 中 `\"auto\"` 是 truthy，所以 `mode_val = \"auto\"`。这看起来没问题。\n\n但让我再检查：当从\"局部\"切回\"自动\"时，前端的调用链：\n\n1. 用户选\"局部\" → `onWbModeChange('local')` → `setWhiteBalanceMode('manual')` → 后端设为 manual\n2. 用户选\"自动\" → `onWbModeChange('auto')` → `setWhiteBalanceMode('auto')` → 后端设为 auto\n\n看起来逻辑是对的。让我检查是否有其他地方干扰。\n\n检查是否有定时器或区域搜索在后台运行，导致模式被覆盖："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_856710c692804eceada103c2","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":1346,"path":"astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":92810,"output":222,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93032,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783412307256,"responseId":"cht000dc8da@dx19f3ba930f329c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4ec84d9","parentId":"95454491","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:19:39.855Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_856710c692804eceada103c2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// v8.41: 白平衡定时器\r\nfunction updateWbTimerInput(input) {\r\n    input.value = input.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction updateFocusTimerInput(input) {\r\n    input.value = input.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, '');\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction toggleWbTimer() {\r\n    var toggle = document.getElementById('wbTimerToggle');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('wbTimerInput');\r\n    if (!toggle || !input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        toggle.checked = false;\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    if (toggle.checked) {\r\n        var region = localStorage.getItem('region_whitebalance');\r\n        if (!region) {\r\n            toggle.checked = false;\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n            return;\r\n        }\r\n        stopWbTimer();\r\n        wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n        updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n        wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n            wbTimerSeconds--;\r\n            updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n            if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n                clearInterval(wbTimerId);\r\n                wbTimerId = null;\r\n                executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\r\n            }\r\n        }, 1000);\r\n        showToast('success', '白平衡定时已启动: ' + minutes + '分钟');\r\n    } else {\r\n        stopWbTimer();\r\n        showToast('info', '白平衡定时已关闭');\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nfunction toggleFocusTimer() {\r\n    var toggle = document.getElementById('focusTimerToggle');\r\n    var input = document.getElementById('focusTimerInput');\r\n    if (!toggle || !input) return;\r\n    var minutes = parseInt(input.value) || 0;\r\n    if (minutes <= 0) {\r\n        toggle.checked = false;\r\n        showToast('warning', '请输入大于0的分钟数');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    if (toggle.checked) {\r\n        var region = localStorage.getItem('region_focus');\r\n        if (!region) {\r\n            toggle.checked = false;\r\n            showToast('warning', '请先框选区域');\r\n\n[670 more lines in file. Use offset=1406 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783412379855}}
{"type":"message","id":"cff4bc68","parentId":"c4ec84d9","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:20:01.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_365d2a82562d4779bf58ef4a","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":80,"offset":1440,"path":"astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":93503,"output":30,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93533,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783412379859,"responseId":"cht000dc19f@dx19f3ba98bda2871503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a7d19e03","parentId":"cff4bc68","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:20:01.471Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_365d2a82562d4779bf58ef4a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    display.textContent = '(' + m + ':' + (s < 10 ? '0' : '') + s + ')';\r\n}\r\n\r\n// v8.40: 定时触发执行（使用保存的选区）\r\nfunction executeScheduledSearch(mode) {\r\n    var regionStr = localStorage.getItem('region_' + mode);\r\n    if (!regionStr) {\r\n        showToast('warning', (mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦') + '无保存选区');\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice;\r\n    if (!dev || !dev.ip) { showToast('error', '未连接设备'); return; }\r\n    var region = JSON.parse(regionStr);\r\n    var endpoint = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-search' : '/api/v1/vision/focus-search';\r\n    var label = mode === 'whitebalance' ? '白平衡' : '对焦';\r\n    showToast('info', label + '定时执行中...');\r\n    operationLog('── ' + label + '定时执行 ──', 'info');\r\n    var body = JSON.stringify({ x: region.x, y: region.y, w: region.w, h: region.h });\r\n    fetch(endpoint, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: body })\r\n        .then(function(resp) {\r\n            if (!resp.ok) throw new Error('HTTP ' + resp.status);\r\n            var reader = resp.body.getReader();\r\n            var decoder = new TextDecoder();\r\n            var buf = '';\r\n            function pump() {\r\n                return reader.read().then(function(r) {\r\n                    if (r.done) return;\r\n                    buf += decoder.decode(r.value, { stream: true });\r\n                    var parts = buf.split('\\n\\n');\r\n                    buf = parts.pop();\r\n                    for (var i = 0; i < parts.length; i++) {\r\n                        var line = parts[i];\r\n                        if (!line.startsWith('data: ')) continue;\r\n                        try {\r\n                            var ev = JSON.parse(line.slice(6));\r\n                            if (ev.type === 'wb' || ev.type === 'focus') {\r\n                                operationLog('调整 #' + ev.step + ': ' + ev.stage + ' R=' + ev.red_gain + ' B=' + ev.blue_gain + ' Δ=' + ev.delta, 'info');\r\n                            } else if (ev.type === 'done') {\r\n                                operationLog('── ' + label + '完成: R=' + ev.final_red + ' B=' + ev.final_blue + ' (' + ev.total_steps + '步) ──', 'success');\r\n                            } else if (ev.type === 'error') {\r\n                                operationLog(label + '错误: ' + ev.message, 'error');\r\n                            }\r\n                        } catch (e) {}\r\n                    }\r\n                    return pump();\r\n                });\r\n            }\r\n            return pump();\r\n        })\r\n        .then(function() {\r\n            // 执行完成后，重新启动定时器\r\n            if (mode === 'whitebalance' && wbTimerId === null) {\r\n                var minutes = parseInt(document.getElementById('wbTimerInput').value) || 0;\r\n                if (minutes > 0) {\r\n                    wbTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n                    updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n                    wbTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n                        wbTimerSeconds--;\r\n                        updateWbTimerDisplay();\r\n                        if (wbTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n                            clearInterval(wbTimerId);\r\n                            wbTimerId = null;\r\n                            executeScheduledSearch('whitebalance');\r\n                        }\r\n                    }, 1000);\r\n                }\r\n            }\r\n            if (mode === 'focus' && focusTimerId === null) {\r\n                var minutes = parseInt(document.getElementById('focusTimerInput').value) || 0;\r\n                if (minutes > 0) {\r\n                    focusTimerSeconds = minutes * 60;\r\n                    updateFocusTimerDisplay();\r\n                    focusTimerId = setInterval(function() {\r\n                        focusTimerSeconds--;\r\n                        updateFocusTimerDisplay();\r\n                        if (focusTimerSeconds <= 0) {\r\n                            clearInterval(focusTimerId);\r\n                            focusTimerId = null;\r\n                            executeScheduledSearch('focus');\r\n                        }\r\n\n[556 more lines in file. Use offset=1520 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783412401471}}
{"type":"message","id":"195d875d","parentId":"a7d19e03","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:20:49.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到了 `executeScheduledSearch`。这个函数执行区域白平衡搜索/对焦。\n\n当用户在局部模式下：1. 运行定时搜索 → 这不会改变设备白平衡模式（只是搜索时的增益调整）\n2. 或者手动运行局部搜索 → 也不会改变设备白平衡模式\n\n所以定时器不会导致问题。\n\n让我再检查 `stopAutoWhiteBalance`：","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"可能是区域搜索在后台运行，导致模式被大量请求覆盖。检查 `stopAutoWhiteBalance` 是否被调用："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3d4600bf87db48058fa9fb68","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":50,"offset":1280,"path":"astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":94713,"output":135,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94848,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783412401473,"responseId":"cht000ddbb2@dx19f3ba9ec8129c2503"}}
{"type":"message","id":"95950349","parentId":"195d875d","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:20:49.713Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3d4600bf87db48058fa9fb68","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 停止自动白平衡\r\nfunction stopAutoWhiteBalance() {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('用户停止', 'warning');\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop', {}).then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n            showToast('success', '已停止白平衡搜索');\r\n        }\r\n    }).catch(function(e) {\r\n        showToast('error', '停止失败');\r\n    });\r\n    // 恢复按钮状态\r\n    var stopBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbLocalStop');\r\n    var confirmBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbTimerConfirm');\r\n    var selectBtn = document.getElementById('btnWbRegionSelect');\r\n    if (stopBtn) stopBtn.disabled = true;\r\n    if (confirmBtn) { confirmBtn.disabled = true; confirmBtn.style.opacity = '0.5'; }\r\n    if (selectBtn) { selectBtn.style.opacity = '1'; }\r\n    selectBtn.style.opacity = '1';\r\n    stopWbTimer();\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 对焦模式切换:显示/隐藏对应控件\r\nfunction onFocusModeChange(mode) {\r\n    var moveControls = document.getElementById('focusMoveControls');\r\n    var localControls = document.getElementById('focusLocalControls');\r\n\r\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        setFocusMode('manual');\r\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\r\n    } else {\r\n        // 自动\r\n        if (moveControls) moveControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\r\n        setFocusMode('auto');\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n// 停止自动对焦\r\nfunction stopAutoFocus() {\r\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\r\n    if (!dev) return;\r\n    if (typeof operationLog === 'function') operationLog('用户停止', 'warning');\r\n    apiPost('/api/v1/vision/focus-stop', {}).then(function(r) {\r\n        if (r && r.success) {\r\n\n[746 more lines in file. Use offset=1330 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783412449713}}
{"type":"message","id":"f8bb24e9","parentId":"95950349","timestamp":"2026-07-07T08:25:26.964Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我先分析：apiPost call to /api/v1/vision/whitebalance-stop only logs and disables UI. It does NOT write back to device. So if a search is active, it's just aborted, but the last gain change from the last step remains in the system until the next RAT (reaction) from a proper ISAPI write. There is no overwrite isolation.在局部执行搜索过程中：1. 每次迭代执行 setWhiteBalanceGain（ISAPI）→ 设备实时状态更新\n2. 最终停止，最后一次 ISAPI 持久保存的值会沉积在设备中\n3. 下一次进入\"自动\"模式时：   - setWhiteBalanceMode('auto') 写入 ISAPI/Device WhiteBalanceStyle=auto\n   - 但如果上一次搜索中已经写入了 manual 模式的 gains，device 状态需要被重置因此我思考：问题可能是 setSearch 前 audit（是否已在自动模式），或者 setSearch 自身覆盖了自动化写回（如 deviceWhitebalanceStyle 已经是 auto），HAS v8.42 guide？实际上如果 device 已经是 auto，再次做 set team 可能：\n- 设置成功（success 返回）\n- 设备保持 auto\n- 但前端逻辑可能错误。\n\n让我检查是否每次 setSearch 调用频道里的手动增益会写回，导致 device 实际被强设为 manual 部分，覆盖了原本 auto 模式的小位，然后下次切换被 client 读取到的 current_mode 是 manual，再次再 auto。实际上新的 ISAPI 明确只更新白平衡模式，不修改增益。但我们现在用的是旧的 ISAPI/old setup，也就是 setWhiteBalance 调用时，XML 同时带 WhiteBalanceStyle 和 gains。所以即使在 auto 模式下调用 mode=auto，如果 sensors 有当前 gains 且未重新使用新 ISAPI 版本，会有一些效应。更好的修复思路：避免 setSearch 干扰 device 自动状态。例如：1) 仅在 search 完的那一步才 commit ISAPI（bind），而不是每一步都 ISAPI write；2) 或者 setSearch 自身封装\"在 search 过程中保持当前模式不变，仅在完成后才提交\"的策略。\n\n实际上用户可用的输出口负责搜索的\"膨胀\"，而 render 函数 controller 负责写 ISAPI。当在局部执行后，r.b（白平衡搜索）的结束一旦冲掉 auto 模式的 gains 和 signature（如果 controller 模式和 useEffect 版本不一致），就会导致下一次切换回 auto 时读取到旧的 gains，hover 失败。更好的办法是：确保 area search 始终保持自动/当前模式不变，对 sensors 追求敏感 altitude：不是 swap 追踪 R/B，而是每一步在同一步要检查当前 device 是否在 auto，若是手动就增加 step bump，每次相等。现在开始构建具体 fix 代码：\n1) 在 setSearch 之前，先读取 device 当前 state，随后宣告它作为备份，在循环的最后一步重置回去；\n2) 修正 frontend：搜索时若 device 已经在 auto，不写入白平衡模式或增调，避免强行强制出模式；\n3) 恢复自动模式回 preprocess，确保后续 '点回自动' 时读取到一致的 auto 标志。\n\n但因老板要求跳过多调逻辑，做事要减少混乱：我们只保留并对此做单点修正。严格控制进入ная输出：唯一改的地方，在 1) 顶端追加一个策略锁（sm. check current mode），2) 概念上确保 setSearch 岛内不修改 persistent ISAPI，3) 后续要是 need 以此收回至最本源（auto）再输出，用 modal 对用户作个 whaler。等等，我先核算一下用户具体说的逻辑：\"主控台，白平衡下拉菜单，点击局部之后，切换到我们的局部算法，但再点击回自动，并没有应用自动\"。意思：\n1) 点\"局部\" → 显示局部控件 → 开始局部搜索 → 设备是否先改回手动？\n2) 点\"自动\" → 应该有'只改模式，搜索结束回 re-enable auto'm Company视觉模式，完成，立即 back to \"auto\"。\n我已经了解了业务逻辑：顶层布局是：顶层主界面是'白平衡搜索'触发，底层是 白平衡下拉框。\n\n所以修复策略应该是：在 setSearch 中，除非显式想改模式，否则只传增益调整，不传模式；只在使用 LOCAL 的设置步骤时才谈 setWhiteBalanceMode 真正行为。\n\n但目前搜索控制器是轮询模式的，且每一帧都写入 ISAPI。在局部模式下，这会写入 gains。如果在 auto 模式下执行的 setIslandming 会错误设入 ISAPI。所以直接修复是在 search 中添加 a bit（检查当前白平衡模式是 auto/手动，仅在 '/')。\n\n用户要求精确，不要打补丁。所以我将做最小动作修复：在otericController的search loop 内，判断当前 device 的白平衡是否为 'manual'，如是，则 add step 进行；如不是，则 step attempt no-operation（实际上不写入 ISAPI）。这可以用一个小函数做 guard：_shouldSearch be manualmode confirm，search only write manual extra updates。但用户不想多乱改，我还假设搜索 loop 是外层的 control panel 调用 R/W。目前应当怎做？\n\n最简点通常是\"在最顶层调用时做 check\"，前端 UI 让 local 用户不选 auto should min cancel the search only once。用户说点击回 auto dos not apply auto，那意味着前端去 true 白平衡控制时，没有确认\"already in manual\"状态而直接 doing，由于逻辑已经改成了仅接收 gains，而没有重置为 auto。\n\n正确的流程应该是：\n1) 点击 auto 下拉 → mode select to 'auto' → 前端 UI 停止所有正在进行的区域搜索和 JS buy payload；\n2) 前端调用 setWhiteBalanceMode('auto') → 后端将 ISAPI 白平衡设为 auto，同时清除当前的增益（如果新 ISAPI API 支持 reset）；\n3) 完成后前端刷新参数 loadWhiteBalance 以同步 UI。\n\n鉴于用户要求不做多余修补，我现在会实现最小的修正点：在 frontend 数据流结构中增加自动化检查，确保当 '点回自动' 时强制重置参数，并在后端返回的白平衡状态时，如果设备正是 auto 模式，就 refresh UI，但需要同步其他两个: search 只在需要时写回 manual。修复思路：\n1) 前端：在 onWbModeChange 中，当选择 auto，取消白色定时下，并在 setSearch 调用前清空 region 区域（不允许区域搜索在实际 auto 模式下运行），进而避免正在进行中搜索与 auto 状态冲突；\n2) 前端：在主入口检查：若选取 local 但设备白平衡已经是 auto，需先 switch 手动再 run search（确保可控）。\n\n用户说\"只修复下拉菜单\"，那我就只修改前端，不要动白平衡搜索与后端的任何代码。\n\n具体修改：\n在 local 切换 fallback manual 时：\n```javascript\n} else if (mode === 'local') {\n    if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\n    if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'block';\n    if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\n    if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\n    // 新增：确认并回滚设备到 manual，再允许运行 search\n    setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\n}\n```\n\n在 auto 切换时：\n```javascript\n} else {\n    // 自动\n    if (manualControls) manualControls.style.display = 'none';\n    if (localControls) localControls.style.display = 'none';\n    if (wbRed) wbRed.disabled = true;\n    if (wbBlue) wbBlue.disabled = true;\n    setWhiteBalanceMode('auto');\n    // 新增：强制刷新参数并清除可能的外部搜索\n    var dev = window.connectedDevice ? window.connectedDevice.ip : null;\n    if (dev) {\n        stopAutoWhiteBalance(); // 停止后台搜索\n        // 强制重新读取白平衡参数，确保设备同步到 auto\n        apiGet('/api/v1/ptz/' + dev + '/image/whitebalance').then(function(r) {\n            if (r && r.success && r.data && r.data.mode === 'auto') {\n                var wbModeSelect = document.getElementById('wbMode');\n                if (wbModeSelect) {\n                    wbModeSelect.value = 'auto';\n                    onWbModeChange('auto');\n                }\n            }\n        });\n    }\n}\n```\n\n修复的核心点是在 auto 切换 URL 远程 device status 分离解耦条件下，通过先 stop autocall，再 force load 同步，避免 state 不一致。\n\n好了，检修完毕。开始实施最精简修复：\n\n**仅前端修改**：\n- 在 auto 分支强制 stopAutoWhiteBalance + 强制重新读设备参数，确保 device 在 auto 模式；\n- 在 local 分支继续保持 write manual，不做多余变化；\n\nexpected:\n1) 用户点局部 → 逻辑与当前一致（search run）\n2) 用户点自动 → 前端先 stop 时序上所有后台搜索，然后调用 ISAPI 写回 auto，再主动获取 device side，confirm 同步后再更新 UI。\n\n输入: console.html onWbModeChange。\n\n行动：\nwrite 一个精简 patch，只改 onWbModeChange，确保在下拉菜单 click 回 auto 时，强制 reap layout 并等待 read做完；切换其他选项时可 watch 逐渐恢复默认走。 targets Goal: 确保每次 selected 后 UI 与 device 一致，不要依赖后续懒加载。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"明白。老板现在的核心要求：\n\n## 当前进度\n- `whitebalance.py` 已完全回滚 ✓\n- 正在排查下拉菜单问题\n- 需要精确修复\"局部→自动\"不生效问题\n\n## 排查结果（根因初步定位）\n\n**前端逻辑**（console.html line 1251-1280）：\n```javascript\nfunction onWbModeChange(mode) {\n    if (mode === 'manual') {\n        manualControls.style.display = 'flex';\n        localControls.style.display = 'none';\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');\n    } else if (mode === 'local') {\n        manualControls.style.display = 'none';\n        localControls.style.display = 'block';\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('manual');  // ← 切到局部后，后端设为手动\n    } else {\n        // 自动\n        manualControls.style.display = 'none';\n        localControls.style.display = 'none';\n        setWhiteBalanceMode('auto');  // ← 重新选自动，调用后端切换\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**后端逻辑**（router.py line 2953-2993）：\n```python\nmode_val = mode_input if mode_input else current_mode\nmode_isapi = mode_val.lower() if mode_val else \"manual\"\nxml_str = f'''...<WhiteBalanceStyle>{mode_isapi}</WhiteBalanceStyle>\n<WhiteBalanceRed>{red_val}</WhiteBalanceRed>\n<WhiteBalanceBlue>{blue_val}</WhiteBalanceBlue>'''\n```\n\n**可能的问题**：\n1. ISAPI `WhiteBalanceStyle` + `WhiteBalanceRed/Blue` 同时写入，导致设备状态被\"锁定\"到最后一次手动增益\n2. 后端 GET 时读取到的 `current_mode` 仍然是 auto，但设备侧已经变成了 manual（红蓝增益值≠100/80）\n3. 再次调用 PUT auto，后端校验 `mode_val = mode_input` = \"auto\" → 写 ISAPI WhiteBalanceStyle=auto，但白底 state imbalance 的 gains 值没被清空\n\n**精确修复方案**（仅前端，最小化改动）：\n在 `onWbModeChange('auto')` 时：\n1. **先**调用 `setWhiteBalanceMode('auto')` 确保设备切换到 auto 模式\n2. **立刻**调用 `loadWhiteBalance(deviceIp)` 重新读取设备参数，确认 UI 已同步\n\n## 即刻执行：修复前端下拉菜单逻辑"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5f5a0d23d3714a7189549bcf","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":10,"offset":1251,"path":"astrohub/src/web/includes/console.html"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"HP","model":"glm-5.2","usage":{"input":95361,"output":2607,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97968,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783412449714,"responseId":"cht000d5ebf@dx19f3baa9f2b2872503"}}
